query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `wings` (
  `id` INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `name` VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  `description` TEXT,
  `type` ENUM('bone-in', 'boneless') NOT NULL,
  `isGlutenFree` BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `wingPrices` (
  `id` INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `wingId` INT NOT NULL,
  `size` ENUM('8pc', '12pc', '20pc', '40pc') NOT NULL,
  `price` DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (`wingId`) REFERENCES `wings`(`id`) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `wingFlavors` (
  `id` INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `name` VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  `isGlutenFree` BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
  `sortOrder` INT DEFAULT 0,
  `createdAt` TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);
